title: BRIEF-AT&T Says At Annual Meeting, Each Of 13 Nominees To Co's Board Were Reelected For 1-Yr Terms
text:
Market News April 27, 2018 / 2:57 PM / in 20 minutes BRIEF-AT&T Says At Annual Meeting, Each Of 13 Nominees To Co's Board Were Reelected For 1-Yr Terms Reuters Staff 1 Min Read
April 27 (Reuters) - AT&T Inc:
* AT&T INC - AT CO’S ANNUAL MEETING OF STOCKHOLDERS, EACH OF 13 NOMINEES TO COMPANY’S BOARD OF DIRECTORS WERE REELECTED FOR ONE-YEAR TERMS
* AT&T INC - SHAREHOLDER PROPOSALS FOR LOBBYING REPORT AND INDEPENDENT CHAIRMAN WERE DEFEATED Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
